title: Miles Davis - Ascenseur pour L'echafaud 1957 TQMP
description:
Yet Another Release from The Quality Music Project! (TQMP)

In this project I share quality items out of my personal CD collection in an uncompressed format for everyone to enjoy. I hope this will encourage others to do the same, so this great network will grow to be the biggest music library worldwide. (Or is it already?)

Ripped as a CD image, so 100% soundquality! Artwork Included.
 
Just burn the .img file using Nero or ImgBurn (freeware) and play.
ImgBurn can be downloaded at: http://www.imgburn.com/index.php?act=download

If you encounter any problem, please comment. Because I only have 25kb/s upload I will upload and seed 1 CD every day. So if the collection serves your taste, it might be useful to check from time to time. You can search using the string TQMP.

Enjoy!
